```py
>>> np.nancumprod(1)
array([1])
>>> np.nancumprod([1])
array([1])
>>> np.nancumprod([1, np.nan])
array([1.,  1.])
>>> a = np.array([[1, 2], [3, np.nan]])
>>> np.nancumprod(a)
array([1.,  2.,  6.,  6.])
>>> np.nancumprod(a, axis=0)
array([[1.,  2.],
 [3.,  2.]])
>>> np.nancumprod(a, axis=1)
array([[1.,  2.],
 [3.,  3.]]) 
```
